long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Are you finding it difficult to keep track of which multiplication facts were passed? This App is for students who need to practice and pass their multiplication facts 2-10. Students can create a profile and take the 1-minute quizzes until they pass. Each quiz has 10 multiplication facts to pass. Once you pass each quiz, you can take a different one. The final quiz is a mixed multiplication quiz of 50 problems in 3 minutes. Teachers can monitor the students' quizzes and students can take the final mixed quiz for $2.99 subscription for the year.
